org.petuum.jbosen.row

Interface RowUpdate

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DoubleRowUpdate, FloatRowUpdate, IntRowUpdate, LongRowUpdate
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DenseDoubleRowUpdate, DenseFloatRowUpdate, DenseIntRowUpdate, DenseLongRowUpdate, SparseDoubleRowUpdate, SparseFloatRowUpdate, SparseIntRowUpdate, SparseLongRowUpdate

    public interface RowUpdate
    This interface specifies a row update for a Bosen PS table. An implementation of this interface does not need to be thread-safe.
